John, old friend, it is good to see you back on these threads.<br><br>
You and I share the same profession. I have been at it for 25 years now, and I am painfully aware of the type of circumstance you describe. I grieve for your misfortune, but I know you have an inner strength to pull through.<br><br>
We hold within us the power of ourselves, our self esteem, our way in this world. Finding it is the problem. As you can see from my words here, I still struggle with many fundimental issues. I am still on a path of discovery and learning. I do, however, have my honor. Upon that I must build. <br><br>
John, you are welcome here.<br><br>
I hope you will stay for a while.<br><br>
Heed the words of Humming Eagle, and study them carefully.<br><br>
His Tunkasila have great wisdom! 
